Fwikileaks-founder-julian-assanges-long-fight-against-extradition-to-us-5963209%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fwikileaks-founder-julian-assanges-long-fight-against-extradition-to-us-5963209%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BThey%20Changed%20Their%20Plan%2C%20So%20I%20Realised...%26quot%3B%3A%20How%20Rohit%20Outsmarted%20Australia%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EWinning%20was%20not%20a%20'breeze'%20for%20India%20in%20their%20last%20T20%20World%20Cup%20Super%20Eight%20match%20against%20Australia%20as%20skipper%20Rohit%20Sharma%20said%20he%20had%20to%20tweak%20his%20batting%20to%20take%20the%20wind%20out%20of%20the%202021%20champions'%20sails.%20Rohit%20played%20some%20delectable%20strokes%20on%20the%20off%20side%20as%20the%20'Player%20of%20the%20Match'%20made%20a%20match-winning%2092%20off%20just%2041%20deliveries%20just%20when%20his%20opening%20partner%20Virat%20Kohli%20departed%20for%20a%20duck.%20Courtesy%20Rohit's%20seven%20boundaries%20and%20eight%20sixes%2C%20India%20scored%20205%2F5%20and%20then%20restricted%20Mitchell%20Marsh's%20side%20to%20181%2F7%20for%20a%2024-run%20victory%20and%20moved%20into%20the%20semifinal%20of%20the%20showpiece%20event.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20wind%20a%20perpetual%20hindrance%2C%20Rohit%20said%20he%20had%20to%20play%20more%20strokes%20on%20the%20off%20side%20to%20negate%20the%20impact.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20thought%20right%20from%20over%20number%20one%2C%20there%20was%20a%20strong%20breeze%20blowing%20across.%20They%20(Australia)%20changed%20their%20plan%2C%20bowling%20against%20the%20breeze%2C%20so%20I%20realised%20I%20had%20to%20open%20up%20the%20off%20side%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou've%20got%20to%20factor%20in%20the%20breeze%20and%20understand%20that%20the%20bowlers%20are%20smart%20as%20well%20and%20open%20up%20all%20sides%20of%20the%20field.%20When%20you%20keep%20an%20open%20mind%20and%20not%20just%20think%20of%20one%20shot%2C%20you%20can%20access%20all%20areas%20of%20the%20field%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20India%20skipper%20after%20the%20match.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B200%20is%20obviously%20a%20good%20score%2C%20but%20when%20you're%20playing%20on%20grounds%20like%20this%20where%20wind%20is%20a%20factor%2C%20anything%20is%20possible%2C%20but%20I%20thought%20we%20used%20the%20conditions%20very%20well.%20It%20was%20very%20pleasing%20to%20see%20how%20we%20were%20getting%20through%20those%20overs%20and%20getting%20the%20wickets%20at%20the%20same%20time.%26quot%3B%20Rohit%20also%20said%20he%20knew%20wrist-spinner%20Kuldeep%20Yadav%20would%20be%20at%20his%20potent%20best%20in%20the%20West%20Indies%20after%20encountering%20seamer-friendly%20conditions%20in%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKuldeep%20returned%20excellent%20figures%20of%202%2F24%20in%20his%20four%20overs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BKuldeep%2C%20we%20understand%20the%20strengths%20he%20has%2C%20but%20you%20have%20to%20use%20it%20when%20you%20need%20it.%20The%20pitches%20in%20New%20York%20were%20seamer-friendly%2C%20but%20we%20knew%20he%20would%20play%20a%20big%20role%20later.%26quot%3B%20Rohit%20categorically%20said%20he%20was%20concentrating%20only%20on%20maintaining%20the%20%26quot%3Btempo%26quot%3B%20of%20the%20match%20and%20not%20bothering%20one%20bit%20about%20his%20century.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20a%20good%20wicket%2C%20and%20you%20want%20to%20try%20and%20back%20yourself%20to%20play%20those%20kinds%20of%20shots.%20I've%20been%20trying%20to%20do%20that%20for%20a%20few%20years%20now%2C%20and%20I'm%20glad%20it%20came%20off%20today.%20The%20fifties%20and%20hundreds%20don't%20matter%2C%20I%20wanted%20to%20bat%20with%20the%20same%20tempo%20and%20carry%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20want%20to%20make%20big%20scores%2C%20yes%2C%20but%20at%20the%20same%20time%20you%20want%20to%20make%20the%20bowlers%20think%20where%20the%20next%20shot%20is%20coming%2C%20and%20I%20think%20I%20managed%20to%20do%20that%20today%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20skipper%20added%20that%20would%20like%20India%20to%20continue%20playing%20the%20same%20way%20in%20the%20knockouts%20in%20the%20manner%20they%20have%20played%20so%20far.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20don't%20want%20to%20do%20anything%20different%20(in%20the%20knockouts).%20We%20want%20to%20play%20the%20same%20way%2C%20understand%20what%20the%20individuals%20need%20to%20do%20in%20a%20given%20situation%2C%20and%20play%20freely.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20far%20we've%20been%20doing%20that%20consistently%2C%20and%20semifinals%2C%20we%20have%20to%20try%20and%20do%20the%20same%20thing.%20It'll%20be%20nice%20(to%20play%20England%20in%20the%20semifinal).%20Nothing%20changes%20for%20us%2C%20we%20want%20to%20focus%20on%20what%20we%20can%20do%20as%20a%20team%2C%20and%20take%20the%20game%20on.%26quot%3B%20Australian%20skipper%20Mitchell%20Marsh%2C%20who%20was%20guilty%20of%20grassing%20a%20sitter%20and%20could%20not%20build%20on%20his%20good%20start%20with%20the%20bat%2C%20conceded%20India%20were%20better%20on%20the%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20disappointing.%20Still%20technically%20a%20chance%20to%20go%20through%2C%20and%20today%20India%20got%20the%20better%20of%20us.%20I%20think%20over%20the%20course%20of%2040%20overs%20there's%20a%20lot%20of%20small%20margins%2C%20but%20honestly%2C%20India%20were%20the%20better%20team.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe've%20seen%20for%2015%20years%20what%20Rohit%20Sharma%20can%20do%20in%20that%20kind%20of%20mood%2C%20and%20he%20got%20off%20to%20an%20absolute%20flier.%20In%20a%20run%20chase%20like%20that%2C%20you're%20in%20it%20if%20you%20can%20keep%20it%20at%20tens%20(10%20runs%20per%20over)%20for%20as%20long%20as%20possible%2C%20but%20India%20were%20too%20good%20for%20us.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C