ariety-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fvariety.com%2F2024%2Ftv%2Fnews%2Fjosh-duggar-appeal-rejected-19-kids-and-counting-1236047418%2Famp%2F%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2024%2Ftv%2Fnews%2Fjosh-duggar-appeal-rejected-19-kids-and-counting-1236047418%2Famp%2F%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Relationship%20Between%20India%2C%20US%20Is%20Multiplicative%3A%20US%20Envoy%20To%20India%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20relationship%20between%20India%20and%20the%20US%20is%20not%20just%20%26quot%3Baddictive%26quot%3B%2C%20it%20is%20%26quot%3Bmultiplicative%26quot%3B%2C%20US%20envoy%20to%20India%20Eric%20Garcetti%20has%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGarcetti%20also%20said%20that%20the%20relationship%20between%20the%20two%20countries%20has%20never%20been%20so%20good.%20The%20Indian-American%20community%20is%20the%20most%20successful%20immigrant%20community%20in%20America.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20made%20these%20remarks%20on%20Monday%20at%20an%20event%20on%20the%20sidelines%20of%20the%20SelectUSA%20Investment%20Summit%2C%20to%20which%20the%20largest%20delegation%20is%20from%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20(India%20US)%20is%20a%20relationship%20that%20isn't%20just%20additive.%20It's%20not%20just%20the%20US%20plus%20India.%20It's%20multiplicative.%20It's%20the%20United%20States%20times%20India%2C%E2%80%9D%20Garcetti%20said%20on%20the%20sidelines%20of%20the%20summit%2C%20to%20which%20the%20largest%20delegation%20is%20from%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20SelectUSA%20Investment%20Summit%20is%20the%20highest-profile%20event%20in%20the%20US%20to%20facilitate%20business%20investment%20by%20connecting%20thousands%20of%20investors%2C%20companies%2C%20economic%20development%20organisations%20(EDOs)%2C%20and%20industry%20experts%20to%20make%20deals%20happen.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGarcetti%20was%20speaking%20at%20the%20event%20wherein%20India's%20JSW%20Steel%20announced%20its%20plans%20to%20invest%20USD%20140%20million%20in%20Bayton%2C%20Texas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNow%2C%20Americans%20are%20getting%20more%20and%20more%20familiar%20with%20Indian%20brands%20and%20Indian%20companies...%20Together%20we're%20investing%20in%20third%20countries%2C%20infrastructure%2C%20energy%2C%20climate%20solutions%2C%20empowering%20tomorrow's%20prosperity%2C%E2%80%9D%20Garcetti%20said%20as%20he%20announced%20investment%20from%20JW%20Steel%20in%20Texas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20so%20excited%20that%20JSW%20Steel%20is%20announcing%20a%20USD%20140%20million%20investment%20in%20America%2C%20in%20Baytown%2C%20in%20Texas.%20JSW%20is%20one%20of%20the%20largest%20Indian%20investors%20in%20the%20United%20States%2C%20investing%20more%20than%20USD%202%20billion%20here%20in%20this%20country%2C%20in%20Texas%20and%20in%20Ohio.%20They%20have%20seen%20tremendous%20return%20on%20their%20investment%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%20This%20FDI%20would%20result%20in%20jobs%20for%20more%20than%20800%20American%20workers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGarcetti%20also%20said%20that%20the%20relationship%20between%20India%20and%20the%20US%20has%20never%20been%20so%20good.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe've%20never%20had%20a%20closer%20relationship%20with%20India.%20Americans%20of%20Indian%20descent%20are%20now%20about%201.5%25%20of%20our%20population.%20And%20pay%20six%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20taxes%20in%20America.%20It%20is%20the%20most%20successful%20immigrant%20community%20in%20America%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhile%20the%20story%20used%20to%20be%20about%20American%20companies%20going%20to%20India%20to%20invest%2C%20which%20we%20still%20do%2C...%20increasingly%20we're%20seeing%20this%20two-way%20street%2C%20a%20bridge%20in%20the%20Indo-pacific%20coming%20from%20India%20into%20the%20United%20States%2C%20savings%20steel%20mills%2C%20looking%20at%20mines%20that%20have%20been%20shut%20down%2C%20investing%20in%20electrolytes%20for%20electric%20vehicles%20of%20the%20future%2C%20the%20services%2C%20the%20health%20care%2C%E2%80%9D%20Garcetti%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDiane%20Farrell%2C%20Deputy%20Under%20Secretary%20for%20International%20Trade%2C%20from%20the%20Department%20of%20Commerce%20said%20India%20has%20the%20largest%20country%20delegation%20to%20the%20SelectUSA%20Investment%20Summit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDivyakumar%20Bhair%2C%20Board%20Member%2C%20JSW%20Steel%20USA%20said%20that%20these%20investments%20would%20go%20into%20manufacturing%20high-end%20steel%20plates%20which%20are%20used%20for%20offshore%20wind%2C%20monopile%2C%20transition%20pieces%2C%20and%20towers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20will%20not%20only%20help%20realise%20the%20dream%20of%20clean%20energy%20for%20the%20generations%20to%20come%20in%20the%20United%20States%20but%20will%20also%20catalyse%20the%20local%20economies%20of%20Texas%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%20JSW%20USA%20is%20part%20of%20the%20diversified%20USD%2024%20billion%20JSW%20Group.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719277620000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Fhlaj9hvs_us-envoy-eric-garcetti_625x300_14_May_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fus-envoy-to-india-eric-garcetti-says-relationship-between-india-us-is-multiplicative-5963141%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20relationship%20between%20India%20and%20the%20US%20is%20not%20just%20%26quot%3Baddictive%26quot%3B%2C%20it%20is%20%26quot%3Bmultiplicative%26quot%3B%2C%20US%20envoy%20to%20India%20Eric%20Garcetti%20has%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fus-envoy-to-india-eric-garcetti-says-relationship-between-india-us-is-multiplicative-5963141%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fus-envoy-to-india-eric-