fghanistan%2C%20Bangladesh%20To%20Reach%20Semis%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20T20%20World%20Cup%20semi-final%20race%20in%20Group%201%20has%20become%20really%20interesting.%20India%20became%20the%20first%20team%20from%20the%20group%20to%20enter%20the%20semi-finals%20as%20they%20beat%20the%20Mitchell%20March-led%20%C2%A0Australia%20by%2024%20runs%20on%20Monday.%20However%2C%20the%20other%20three%20teams%20in%20the%20group%20are%20not%20out.%20The%20points%20table%20is%20as%20follows%20-%20India%20(6%20points%2C%203%20games%2C%20NRR%20%2B2.017)%2C%20Australia%20(2%20points%2C%203%20games%2C%20NRR%20-0.331)%2C%20Afghanistan%20(2%20points%2C%202%20matches%2C%20NRR%20-0.650)%2C%20Bangladesh%20(0%20points%2C%202%20matches%2C%20NRR%20-2.489).%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20Afghanistan%2C%20Bangladesh%20and%20Australia%20can%20qualify%20for%20semi-finals.%20Following%20are%20the%20scenarios%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E1.%20Afghanistan%20can%20enter%20the%20semi-finals%20with%20a%20win%20over%20Bangladesh.%20That%20way%20they%20will%20reach%204%20points%20and%20be%20the%20second%20team%20from%20Group%201%20of%20Super%208%20to%20enter%20last%20four%20stage.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E2.%20Australia%20can%20enter%20semi-finals%20only%20if%20Afghanistan%20lose%20to%20Bangladesh%20with%20a%20margin%20of%20less%20than%2061%20runs%20(considering%20the%20first%20innings%20total%20is%20160)%20or%20outside%2013%20overs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E3.%20Bangladesh%20can%20enter%20semi-finals%20only%20if%20they%20beat%20Afghanistan%20by%20a%20big%20margin%20(by%2061%20runs%20if%20they%20score%20160%20or%20chase%20the%20target%20in%2013%20overs)%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20Monday's%20match%20that%20Australia%20lost%2C%20India%20rode%20on%20skipper%20Rohit%20Sharma's%20scintillating%2041-ball%2092%20to%20beat%20Australia%20by%2024%20runs%20in%20their%20final%20Super%20Eights%20fixture%20and%20qualify%20for%20the%20semifinals%20of%20the%20T20%20World%20Cup.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBatting%20first%2C%20Rohit%20fired%20on%20all%20cylinders%20and%20struck%20as%20many%20as%20eight%20sixes%20and%20seven%20fours%20during%20his%20sparkling%20knock%2C%20which%20powered%20India%20to%20an%20imposing%20205%20for%20five.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20reply%2C%20Australia%20were%20restricted%20to%20181%20for%20seven%20in%20the%20stipulated%2020%20overs.%20Travis%20Head%20top-scored%20for%20Australia%20with%2076%20off%2043%20balls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20Indian%20bowlers%2C%20Kuldeep%20Yadav%20(2%2F24)%20performed%20brilliantly%20in%20the%20middle%20overs%2C%20while%20Arshdeep%20Singh%20ended%20with%20figures%20of%203%2F37.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20unperturbed%20by%20Virat%20Kohli's%20early%20dismissal%2C%20Rohit%20went%20after%20pacer%20Mitchell%20Starc%20and%20bludgeoned%20him%20for%2029%20runs%20in%20his%20second%20over%2C%20setting%20the%20tone%20for%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStarc%2C%20who%20was%20taken%20to%20the%20cleaners%20by%20Rohit%2C%20returned%20to%20dismiss%20the%20India%20captain%20and%20give%20some%20relief%20to%20the%20Australian%20camp.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20Suryakumar%20Yadav%20(31%20off%2016%20balls)%20and%20Shivam%20Dube%20(28%20off%2022)%20kept%20up%20the%20tempo%20with%20their%20big%20hits%20before%20Hardik%20Pandya%20(27%20off%2017)%20finished%20the%20India%20innings%20in%20style.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20PTI%20inputs%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719277080000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Fp60eibt_afghanistan-vs-australia_625x300_23_June_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ft20-world-cup-2024%2Fhow-can-afghanistan-australia-bangladesh-qualify-for-t20-world-cup-semi-finals-after-indias-win-all-scenarios-5961909%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22T20%20World%20Cup%3A%20India%20became%20the%20first%20team%20from%20the%20group%20to%20enter%20the%20semi-finals%20as%20they%20beat%20the%20Mitchell%20March-led%20Australia%20by%2024%20runs%20on%20Monday.%20However%2C%20the%2