re%E2%80%A6Joe%20Wright%20actually%20did%20that%20on%20%26quot%3BAnna%20Karenina%26quot%3B%20too.%20He%20used%20to%20play%20music%2C%20like%20techno%2C%20over%20the%20scenes%20in%20take%20just%20to%20give%20us%20a%20vibe.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJude%3A%20And%20the%20animals%20on%20set%20obviously%20brought%20their%20own%20odor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWas%20this%20the%20first%20time%20either%20of%20you%20have%20used%20smell%20to%20get%20into%20a%20character%2C%20to%20get%20into%20a%20mindset%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJude%3A%20I%20use%20it%20quite%20a%20lot%20because%2C%20as%20Alicia%20said%2C%20it's%20a%20really%20good%20way%20of...%20You've%20got%20to%20step%20into%20these%20characters%20every%20day.%20And%20so%20sometimes%20if%20you%20can%20do%20something%20that%20just%20is%2C%20not%20really%20a%20shortcut%2C%20but%20it's%20about%20really%20finding%20a%20place.%20It's%20a%20ritual%2C%20and%20it%20can%20just%20put%20you%20in%20a%20certain%20frame%20of%20mind%20or%20mood.%20It%20can%20help%20or%20it%20certainly%20helps%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThere%20are%20a%20lot%20of%20frankly%20kind%20of%20gross%20sex%20scenes%20that%20really%20drive%20home%20just%20the%20unbalanced%2C%20fraught%20nature%20of%20Henry%20and%20Katherine's%20relationship.%20Henry%20had%20previously%20beheaded%20two%20of%20his%20wives%20and%20was%2C%20at%20this%20point%20in%20his%20life%2C%20a%20little%20unstable%2C%20to%20put%20it%20lightly.%20How%20was%20it%20filming%20those%20intimate%20scenes%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJude%3A%20I%20mean%2C%20there's%20always%20a%20certain%20awkwardness%2C%20but%20it's%20also%20hilarious%2C%20I%20mean%2C%20as%20I'm%20remembering%20it.%20There's%20something%20hilarious%20about%20when%20you're%20playing%20someone%20who's%20in%20that%20kind%20of%20physical%20shape%20and%20who%20is%20also%20wielding%20so%20much%20power.%20There%20were%20certain%20moments%20where%20you%20can't%20help%20but%20be%20slightly%20embarrassed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlicia%3A