ing%20advantage%20of%20opportunities%20like%20your%20employer's%20401(k)%20match%2C%20you%20might%20be%20holding%20on%20to%20too%20much%20cash.%20A%20match%2C%20where%20your%20employer%20matches%20your%20401(k)%20contributions%20up%20to%20a%20certain%20percentage%2C%20is%20like%20free%20money%2C%20and%20that%20extra%20money%20from%20your%20checking%20account%20would%20better%20serve%20you%20in%20your%20retirement%20account.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOr%2C%20maybe%20you%20haven't%20considered%C2%A0another%20saving%20or%20investment%20account%20like%20a%20health%20savings%20account%2C%20which%20is%20a%20tax-advantaged%20account%20for%20qualified%20health%20expenses%20that%20you%20can%20roll%20over%20year%20to%20year%20and%20use%20for%20supplemental%20retirement%20savings%20in%20the%20future.%20Anyone%20with%20a%20high-deductible%20healthcare%20plan%20is%20eligible%2C%20and%20some%20extra%20money%20in%20an%20HSA%20would%20make%20more%20progress%20toward%20building%20wealth%20than%20in%20your%20checking%20account.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E5.%20You're%20worried%20you're%20missing%20out%20on%20money%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20average%20checking%20account%20has%20an%20interest%20rate%20of%200.07%25%2C%20according%20to%20the%20FDIC.%20That's%20much%20lower%20than%20the%20typical%20interest%20rate%20on%20a%20high-yield%20savings%20account.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20that%20pales%20in%20comparison%20to%20the%2010%25%20average%20annual%20return%20in%20the%20stock%20market%2C%20meaning%20a%20retirement%20account%20or%20other%20long-term%20investment%20account%20could%20grow%20even%20more.%20By%20leaving%20money%20in%20a%20checking%20account%2C%20you%20could%20be%20missing%20out%20on%20more%20growth.%20If%20that's%20not%20something%20you're%20comfortable%20with%2C%20it's%20time%20to%20move%20it.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI've%20got%20clients%20who%20don't%20think%20they%20have%20too%20much%20in%20their%20checking%20account%2C%26quot%3B%20Bair%20says%2C%20%26quot%3Bbut%20once%20they%20see%20the%20low%20interest%20rate%20that%20they're%20getting%20and%20what%20they%20could%20get%20in%20interest%2C%20we'll%20usually%20move%20some%20over%20into%20that%20next%20level.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20was%20originally%20published%20in%20March%202020.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftoo-much-money-in-checking-account-signs-2024-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719265801000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5e614f66fee23d46d968a408%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftoo-much-money-in-checking-account-signs-2024-6%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Money%20doesn't%20work%20very%20hard%20in%20a%20checking%20account%20%E2%80%94%20moving%20it%20could%20help%20it%20grow%20faster%2C%20earn%20more%20interest%2C%20and%20work%20harder.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Liz%20Knueven)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftoo-much-money-in-checking-account-signs-2024-6%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22My%20partner%20and%20I%20were%20worried%20about%20starting%20a%20business%20together%2C%20but%20it's%20only%20made%20us%20stronger%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226016%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Tawny%20Lara%20and%20her%20partner%20Nick%20drinking%20their%20non-alcoholic%20beverage%2C%20(parentheses)%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66798404d1c84a0eaca70c88%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224016%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETawny%20Lara%20and%20her%20partner%20Nick%20started%20a%20non-alcoholic%20beverage%20brand%20together%20called%20(parentheses).%3Cp%3ERobert%20Riese%20Photography%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EMy%20partner%20and%20I%20started%20a%20non-alcoholic%20drink%20brand%20called%20(parentheses)%20together.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAt%20first%2C%20we%20were%20worried%20about%20working%20together%2C%20and%20didn't%20want%20to%C2%A0'mix%20business%20with%20pleasure.'%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EBut%20our%20relationship%20had%20a%20strong%20foundation%2C%20and%20it%20has%20only%20gotten%20stronger.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAlmost%20all%20business%20books%20will%20tell%20you%20not%20to%20mix%20business%20with%20pleasure.%20We're%20in%20a%20place%20as%20a%20society%20where%20folks%20can%20decide%20which%20axioms%20make%20sense%20for%20our%20own%20lives%20and%20which%20just%20didn't%20age%20well.%20To%20me%2C%20hearing%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cspan%3EDon't%20start%20a%20business%20with%20your%20partner%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cspan%3E%20sounds%20as%20outdated%20as%20%26quot%3BChoose%20a%20company%20with%20a%20good%20pension%2C%20and%20you're%20set%20for%20life.%26quot%3B%20While%20pensions%20are%20a%20relic%20in%20the%20private%20sector%2C%20US%20Census%20data%20shows%20that%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.census.gov%2Fdata%2Ftables%2F2022%2Fecon%2Fabs%2F2022-abs-characteristics-of-businesses.html%3Fmf_ct_campaign%3Dyahoo-synd-feed%26utm_content%3Dsyndication%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E10%25%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20of%20American%20businesses%20are%20owned%20by%20couples.%20My%20husband%20and%20I%20are%20in%20that%2010%25%20%E2%80%94%20and%20we're%20stronger%20than%20ever.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ECountless%20couples%2C%20friends%2C%20and%20family%20members%20run%20successful%20businesses%20together.%20Complications%20are%20bound%20to%20arise%20from%20all%20interpersonal%20relationship%20dynamics%2C%20so%20why%20not%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fquit-my-job-start-company-with-boyfriend-break-up-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Estart%20a%20business%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20with%20someone%20who%20knows%20you%20inside%20and%20out%3F%20Someone%20who%20understands%20your%20tendency%20to%20bite%20off%20more%20than%20you%20can%20chew%20or%20knows%20which%20activities%20help%20you%20relax%20or%20possess%20the%20skills%20and%20knowledge%20that%20are%20so%20complementary%20to%20yours%20that%20you%20decided%20to%20make%20them%20your%20person%20until%20death%20do%20you%20part.%20For%20all%20the%20aforementioned%20reasons%2C%20starting%20a%20business%20with%20my%20husband%20has%20actually%20strengthened%20our%20relationship.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f750501e-bd19-44e9-84dd-67427edbfeb8%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%20tried%20not%20to%20work%20together%2C%20but%20realized%20it%20was%20a%20great%20fit%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENick%20and%20I%20actively%20tried%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3Enot%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cspan%3E%20to%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdating-couple-started-business-failed-relationship-married-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ework%20together%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20because%20we%20obviously%20both%20knew%20that%20mixing%20business%20with%20pleasure%20could%20be%20risky.%20But%20hey%2C%20starting%20a%20business%20is%20one%20of%20the%20riskiest%20adventures%20anyway.%20Go%20hard%20or%20go%20home%2C%20right%3F%20We%20built%20such%20a%20strong%20foundation%20as%20a%20couple%20that%20the%20possibility%20of%20anything%2C%20especially%20work%2C%20breaking%20down%20our%20bond%20felt%20overwhelming.%20Then%20we%20asked%20ourselves%20an%20important%20question%3A%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3EWho%20else%20could%20sell%20this%20extremely%20niche%20seaweed%20vinegar%20non-alcoholic%20drink%20we%20created%20but%20us%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cspan%3E%20That%20realization%20gave%20us%20the%20courage%20to%20start%20a%20business%20together.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%20started%20a%20non-alcoholic%20drink%20brand%20called%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.drinkparentheses.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E(parentheses)%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20was%20born%20out%20of%20our%20own%20personal%20recovery%20journeys.%20Nick%20and%20I%20met%20in%20an%20AA%20meeting%20when%20we%20both%20had%20a%20few%20years%20of%20sobriety%20under%20our%20belts.%20Those%20years%20before%20we%20met%20(and%20after!)%20were%20filled%20with%20peer%20support%20and%20mental%20health%20support%2C%20unpacking%20why%20we%20each%20relied%20on%20alcohol%20so%20heavily%20in%20the%20past.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20addition%20to%20my%20personal%20experience%2C%20I%20spent%20years%20researching%2C%20studying%2C%20and%20interviewing%20people%20about%20how%20their%20relationship%20patterns%20intersect%20with%20their%20alcohol%20use%20while%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penguinrandomhouse.com%2Fbooks%2F730665%2Fdry-humping-by-tawny-lara%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ewriting%20a%20book.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Nick%20and%20I%2C%20like%20many%20of%20my%20subjects%2C%20dealt%20with%20the%20emotional%20upheaval%20and%20required%20boundary-setting%20that%20often%20comes%20from%20changing%20one's%20relationship%20with%20alcohol.%20After%20going%20through%20emotional%20hell%20and%20back%2C%20creating%20a%20marketing%20plan%20together%20or%20debating%20over%20bottle%20sizes%20just%20isn't%20that%20big%20of%20a%20deal.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%229d2c8ceb-1c4c-48de-ac4b-82ed03676beb%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ECommunication%20is%20key%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIndividually%2C%20we've%20learned%20healthy%20coping%20skills%20%E2%80%94%20many%20of%20which%20can%20be%20distilled%20into%20one%20word%3A%20communication.%20Learning%20how%20to%20communicate%20before%20we%20met%20each%20other%20makes%20us%20a%20strong%20couple%3B%20identifying%20and%20accommodating%20our%20individual%20communication%20styles%20makes%20us%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-love-your-business-and-partner-2021-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eexcellent%20business%20partners%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EClear%20communication%20only%20works%20when%20you%20trust%20the%20person%20you're%20communicating%20with.%20How%20clear%20can%20your%20communication%20be%20without%20honesty%3F%20Nick%20and%20I%20learned%20that%20admitting%20that%20we%20needed%20to%20reevaluate%20our%20relationships%20with%20booze%20requires%20a%20great%20deal%20of%20honesty%20with%20ourselves%20and%20others%20%E2%80%94%20a%20virtue%20we%20bring%20into%20the%20ethos%20of%20our%20business.%20That%20humility%20also%20taught%20us%20an%20even%20more%20valuable%20lesson%3A%20It's%20OK%20to%20ask%20for%20help.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%20ask%20for%20help%20all%20the%20time%2C%20both%20as%20a%20couple%20and%20as%20business%20partners.%20Whether%20asking%20for%20assistance%20with%20a%20project%20or%20getting%20advice%20from%20people%20more%20established%20in%20our%20industry%2C%20we%20don't%20feel%20%26quot%3Bweak%26quot%3B%20for%20knowing%20we%20can't%20do%20it%20all.%20We%20know%20which%20skills%20we%20each%20have%2C%20which%20skills%20the%20other%20has%2C%20and%20which%20skills%20we%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmillionaire-parent-outsource-parenting-tasks-virtual-assistant-laundry-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eneed%20to%20outsource%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20or%20learn.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHaving%20self-awareness%20about%20what%20we%20each%20bring%20to%20the%20table%20helps%20us%20work%20more%20efficiently%20(and%20happily!).%20Being%20stubborn%20just%20doesn't%20work.%20Trust%20us%3B%20we've%20tried.%20We%20often%20joke%20that%20Nick%20would%20rather%20be%20covered%20in%20vinegar-mother%20slime%20while%20making%20our%20drink%2C%20and%20I'd%20much%20rather%20make%20a%20TikTok%20of%20him%20covered%20in%20said%20slime.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20arduous%20work%20we%20do%20in%20our%20personal%20recovery%20programs%20teaches%20us%20to%20focus%20on%20what%20we%20can%20control.%20We%20bring%20this%20mindful%20life%20approach%20to%20running%20a%20small%20business%2C%20too.%20We%20can%20control%20producing%20our%20small-batch%2C%20artisanal%20product%20and%20creating%20intentional%20marketing%20plans%2C%20so%20that's%20where%20the%20bulk%20of%20our%20energy%20goes.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%20can't%20control%20that%20we're%20an%20indie%20brand%20swimming%20in%20a%20sea%20of%20VC-backed%20brands.%20We%20also%20can't%20control%20who%20likes%20or%20dislikes%20our%20drink.%20There%20will%20always%20be%20drink%20brands%20with%20more%20capital%20and%20stores%20that%20don't%20want%20to%20sell%20our%20product.%20The%20trick%20to%20staying%20(relatively)%20sane%20when%20working%20with%20your%20spouse%20or%20romantic%20partner%20is%20finding%20the%20nuggets%20of%20controllability%20when%20life%20happens%20on%20life's%20terms.%20Those%20nuggets%20also%20lead%20to%20forming%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fways-methods-build-maintain-lasting-strong-bond-partner-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Estronger%20bond%20as%20a%20couple%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20most%20important%20aspect%20of%20running%20a%20business%20with%20a%20spouse%20or%20partner%20is%20knowing%20when%20to%20clock%20out%20to%20make%20time%20for%20life's%20other%20pleasures.%20There%20are%20evenings%20when%20we%20both%20feel%20defeated%20after%20a%20day%20filled%20with%20low%20sales%20or%20getting%20lost%20in%20bureaucratic%20red%20tape%20with%20the%20Department%20of%20Agriculture%20that%20makes%20us%20want%20to%20scratch%20our%20eyes%20out.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20we%20have%20each%20other%2C%20a%20beautiful%20home%2C%20and%20fur%20babies%20who%20remind%20us%20that%20being%20silly%20can%20alleviate%20much%20of%20life's%20stressors.%20We%20have%20our%20healthy%2C%20learned%20coping%20skills.%20And%20we%20have%20a%20nice%20drink%20to%20sip%2C%20reminding%20us%20why%20we%20decided%20to%20sell%20this%20thing%20in%20the%20first%20place.%20Running%20a%20business%2C%20especially%20with%20your%20partner%2C%20is%20one%20day%20at%20a%20time%2C%20too.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstarting-business-with-partner-strengthened-relationship-2024-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719265741000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6679847750b021b5cae8b2bd%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstarting-business-with-partner-strengthened-relationship-2024-6%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22My%20partner%20and%20I%20started%20a%20non-alcoholic%20drink%20brand%20together%2C%20and%20our%20business%20made%20our%20relationship%20even%20stronger.%20Communication%20is%20key.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Tawny%20Lara)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstarting-business-with-partner-strengthened-relationship-2024-6%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Why%20the%20CMO%20is%20%26quot%3Bthe%20voice%20of%20the%20customer%2C%26quot%3B%20according%20to%20Lenovo%20CMO%20Emily%20Ketchen%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.jwplayer.com%2Fplayers%2FlW08CnOE-jZbcmOYf.html%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22100%25%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Why%20the%20CMO%20is%20%26quot%3Bthe%20voice%20of%20the%20customer%2C%26quot%3B%20according%20to%20Lenovo%2