Sexual%20Intent%26quot%3B%3A%20High%20Court%20On%20Man%20Accused%20Of%20Stripping%2C%20Assaulting%20Boys%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Bombay%20High%20Court%20has%20granted%20bail%20to%20a%2033-year-old%20man%20accused%20of%20assaulting%20three%20minor%20boys%20on%20their%20private%20parts%20on%20suspicion%20of%20being%20thieves%2C%20noting%20that%20there%20was%20no%20sexual%20intent%20involved%20in%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20single%20bench%20of%20Justice%20Anil%20Kilor%2C%20in%20an%20order%20dated%20June%2021%20and%20made%20available%20on%20Monday%2C%20granted%20bail%20to%20Kapil%20Taak.%20The%20court%20noted%20that%20the%20case%20pertained%20solely%20to%20physical%20and%20mental%20torture.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETaak%20was%20arrested%20in%202021%20on%20charges%20of%20unnatural%20offence%2C%20assault%2C%20and%20criminal%20intimidation%20under%20the%20Indian%20Penal%20Code%2C%20as%20well%20as%20for%20sexual%20assault%20under%20the%20Protection%20of%20Children%20from%20Sexual%20Offences%20(POCSO)%20Act.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETaak%20and%20the%20other%20accused%20allegedly%20stripped%20the%20three%20teenage%20boys%2C%20assaulted%20them%20with%20leather%20belts%2C%20inserted%20fingers%20into%20their%20anus%2C%20and%20applied%20balm%20to%20their%20private%20parts.%20Taak%20is%20also%20accused%20of%20filming%20the%20incident%20on%20a%20mobile%20phone.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAfter%20going%20through%20the%20FIR%20and%20the%20allegations%20made%20in%20the%20FIR%20against%20the%20applicant%2C%20prima%20facie%20nothing%20is%20brought%20on%20record%20to%20show%20that%20there%20was%20any%20sexual%20intent%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20bench%20stated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20emphasised%20that%20the%20case%20involved%20%26quot%3Bphysical%20and%20mental%20torture%20meted%20out%20to%20the%20minor%20victims%26quot%3B%20as%20Taak%20and%20the%20other%20accused%20believed%20the%20victims%20were%20thieves.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETaak's%20advocate%20Sana%20Khan%20argued%20that%20the%20provisions%20of%20the%20POCSO%20would%20not%20apply%20in%20this%20case%20as%20there%20was%20no%20sexual%20intent.%20She%20pointed%20out%20that%20Taak%20had%20been%20languishing%20in%20jail%20since%202021%2C%20and%20a%20chargesheet%20in%20the%20case%20has%20already%20been%20filed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20complaint%20against%20Taak%20and%20others%20was%20lodged%20by%20the%20mother%20of%20one%20of%20the%20minor%20victims%20in%20April%20202%20after%20she%20noticed%20some%20people%20watching%20a%20video%20where%20some%20minor%20boys%20were%20being%20assaulted%20and%20abused%20in%20their%20private%20parts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20woman%20identified%20one%20of%20the%20boys%20as%20her%20son.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20the%20complaint%2C%20the%20accused%20persons%20had%20forced%20the%20boys%20to%20accompany%20them%20from%20a%20local%20market%20and%20taken%20them%20to%20a%20secluded%20spot%20where%20they%20were%20assaulted.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719253140000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2F4d6orptg_bombay-high-court-_625x300_14_June_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbombay-high-court-on-man-accused-of-stripping-assaulting-boys-no-sexual-intent-5958453%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Bombay%20High%20Court%20has%20granted%20bail%20to%20a%2033-year-old%20man%20accused%20of%20assaulting%20three%20minor%20boys%20on%20their%20private%20parts%20on%20suspicion%20of%20being%20thieves%2C%20noting%20that%20there%20was%20no%20sexual%20intent%20involved%20in%20the%20case.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbombay-high-court-on-man-accused-of-stripping-assaulting-boys-no-sexual-intent-5958453%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22ht