0I%20will%20meet%20people%20directly%2C%E2%80%9D%20Mr%20Majhi%20asserted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20got%20an%20opportunity%20today%20to%20be%20happy%20and%20we%20should%20celebrate%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%2C%20recalling%20his%20childhood%20days%20when%20he%20used%20to%20visit%20the%20weekly%20market%20at%20Jhumpura%20with%20his%20mother.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Chief%20Minister%20said%20as%20promised%20in%20the%20BJP%20manifesto%2C%20his%20priority%20is%20to%20provide%20Rs%203%2C100%20per%20quintal%20of%20paddy%20as%20MSP%20from%20the%20Kharif%20season.%20He%20also%20said%20Rs%2050%2C000%20will%20be%20paid%20to%20every%20eligible%20woman%20under%20the%20Subhadra%20Yojana.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENoting%20that%20Keonjhar%20is%20rich%20in%20natural%20resources%2C%20Mr%20Majhi%20said%20his%20dream%20is%20to%20build%20a%20%E2%80%9Csunehra%20(golden)%20Kanojhar%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20can%20build%20a%20developed%20Keonjhar%20if%20we%20have%20the%20determination%20to%20do%20so%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(This%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20auto-generated%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719251400000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Fu708ki6g_-mohan-charan-majhi_625x300_15_June_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnew-odisha-chief-minister-mohan-charan-majhi-attempt-made-to-kill-me-during-bjd-regime-5961339%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Odisha%20Chief%20Minister%20Mohan%20Charan%20Majhi%20on%20Monday%20alleged%20there%20was%20an%20attempt%20to%20kill%20him%20during%20the%20regime%20of%20the%20previous%20BJD%20government%20by%20hurling%20bombs.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnew-odisha-chief-minister-mohan-charan-majhi-attempt-made-to-kill-me-during-bjd-regime-5961339%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnew-odisha-chief-minister-mohan-charan-majhi-attempt-made-to-kill-me-during-bjd-regime-5961339%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnew-odisha-chief-minister-mohan-charan-majhi-attempt-made-to-kill-me-during-bjd-regime-5961339%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Jammu%20Paper%20Leak%20%26quot%3BKingpin%26quot%3B%20Under%20Scanner%20Amid%20NEET-NET%20Row%3A%20Sources%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAn%20alleged%20kingpin%20of%20a%20paper%20leak%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20is%20being%20probed%20by%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20to%20see%20if%20he%20has%20links%20to%20the%20irregularities%20in%20the%20NEET-UG%20and%20UGC-NET%20exams.%20Yatin%20Yadav%2C%20the%20alleged%20mastermind%20of%20the%202022%20JKSSB%20sub-inspector%20recruitment%20exam%20paper%20leak%20was%20arrested%20by%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20or%20ED%20today%20as%20part%20of%20a%20money%20laundering%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20ED%20sources%2C%20it%20is%20being%20investigated%20whether%20Yadav%20has%20any%20connection%20to%20the%20paper%20leak%20cases%20of%20the%20key%20examinations%20that%20have%20hit%20headlines%20recently.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ED%20probe%20stems%20from%20a%20CBI%20First%20Information%20Report%20and%20chargesheet%20against%20Yadav%2C%20a%20suspected%20tout%2C%20and%20some%20others.%20The%20ED%20sources%20claimed%20that%20being%20the%20%26quot%3Bkingpin%26quot%3B%20of%20the%20alleged%20paper%20leak%20gang%2C%20Yadav%20executed%20a%20well-crafted%20plan%20involving%20other%20accused%20touts%20based%20in%20Haryana%20and%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20to%20arrange%20candidates%20willing%20to%20access%20the%20leaked%20paper%20against%20payments%20ranging%20from%20Rs%2015%20lakh%20to%20Rs%2030%20lakh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20Service%20Selection%20Board%20(JKSSB)%20sub-inspector%20recruitment%20exam%20was%20held%20on%20March%2027%2C%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20exam%2C%20the%20payments%20-%20mainly%20in%20cash%20-%20collected%20from%20the%20aspirants%20were%20routed%20to%20Yadav's%20bank%20accounts%2C%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ED%20had%20earlier%20attached%20Yadav's%20bank%20accounts%2C%20a%20company%20called%20New%20Global%20Fumigation%20Corporation%20and%20assets%20of%20some%20others%20worth%20Rs%201%20crore%20under%20the%20provisions%20of%20the%20Prevention%20of%20Money%20Laundering%20Act%20(PMLA)%20as%20part%20of%20its%20probe.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20arrest%20comes%20at%20a%20time%20when%20allegations%20of%20irregularities%20in%20the%20conduct%20of%20the%20National%20Eligibility-cum-Entrance%20Test-Undergraduate%20(NEET-UG)%20and%20the%20University%20Grants%20Commission-National%20Eligibility%20Test%20(UGC-NET)%20have%20rocked%20the%20country%2C%20leading%20to%20the%20Centre%20handing%20over%20their%20investigation%20to%20the%20CBI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CBI%20is%20looking%20into%20the%20allegations%20of%20malpractice%20in%20both%20exams%20conducted%20by%20the%20National%20Testing%20Agency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Centre%20on%20Saturday%20replaced%20NTA%20Director%20General%20Subodh%20Singh%20and%20handed%20over%20the%20probe%20into%20irregularities%20in%20NEET-UG%20to%20the%20CBI%2C%20which%20is%20now%20probing%20a%20total%20of%20six%20cases%20in%20the%20matter.%20Pradeep%20Singh%20Kharola%20took%20the%20additional%20charge%20of%20NTA%20on%20Monday%20and%20had%20meetings%20with%20officials%20of%20the%20testing%20body.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Education%20Ministry%20had%20also%20set%20up%20a%20seven-member%20panel%20headed%20by%20former%20ISRO%20chief%20K%20Radhakrishnan%20to%20review%20the%20NTA's%20functioning.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719251160000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Fqh8snf18_yatin-yadav_625x300_24_June_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2