m%20Bapatla%20(Telugu%20Desam%20Party)%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20I%20entered%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20for%20the%20first%20time%20today%2C%20I%20was%20getting%20goosebumps%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20T%20Krishna%20Prasad%2C%20a%20former%20top%20cop%20who%20won%20the%20battle%20for%20Bapatla%20from%20Chandrababu%20Naidu's%20Telugu%20Desam%20Party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20a%20very%20different%20experience...%20I%20had%20never%20thought%20that%20I%20would%20become%20a%20Lok%20Sabha%20MP.%20I%20want%20to%20work%20for%20the%20welfare%20of%20the%20people%20on%20a%20larger%20scale.%20I%20will%20do%20it%20as%20a%20Lok%20Sabha%20MP%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20the%20Director%20General%20of%20Police%20of%20Telangana.%20During%20my%20tenure%20as%20DGP%2C%20I%20realised%20that%20I%20had%20to%20work%20in%20public%20service%20and%20this%20should%20be%20done%20actively.%20That%20is%20why%20I%20have%20joined%20politics%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20MP%20who%20ran%20an%20NGO%20that%20donated%20critical%20equipment%20at%20the%20peak%20of%20the%20Covid-19%20pandemic.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20former%20Telangana-cadre%20IPS%20officer%20who%20retired%20in%202022%2C%20had%20initially%20joined%20the%20BJP%20but%20switched%20to%20TDP%20ahead%20of%20the%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EManish%20Jaiswal%20from%20Hazaribagh%20(BJP)%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFirst-time%20BJP%20MP%20Manish%20Jaiswal%20from%20Hazaribagh%20Sadar%20found%20his%20first%20day%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%20an%20intensely%20emotional%20one.%20%26quot%3BMy%20father%20was%20also%20in%20politics...%20today%20when%20I%20entered%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20for%20the%20first%20time%2C%20I%20felt%20that%20my%20father's%20wish%20had%20been%20fulfilled%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Jaiswal%2C%20a%20two-time%20MLA%2C%20had%20replaced%20the%20BJP's%20sitting%20MP%20and%20former%20minster%20Jayant%20Sinha%20from%20the%20seat.%20Mr%20Sinha%20is%20the%20son%20of%20former%20BJP%20stalwart%20Yashwant%20Sinha%2C%20who%20was%20a%20minister%20in%20the%20government%20led%20by%20Atal%20Bihari%20Vajpayee.%20In%20their%20absence%2C%20their%20family%20borough%20Hazaribagh%20saw%20a%20contest%20between%20two%20candidates%20from%20Other%20Backward%20Classes%20--%20Mr%20Jaiswal%20and%20Congress's%20Jai%20Prakash%20Bhai%20Patel.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20is%20a%20lot%20of%20backwardness%20and%20poverty%20in%20the%20villages%20of%20Hazaribagh.%20There%20has%20been%20a%20lot%20of%20displacement%20there.%20I%20will%20strongly%20put%20forward%20the%20need%20for%20development%20there%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHarender%20Mallik%20from%20Muzaffarnagar%20(Samajwadi%20Party)%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20Harendra%20Mallik%2C%20the%20General%20Secretary%20of%20Akhilesh%20Yadav's%20Samajwadi%20Party%2C%20the%20first%20visit%20to%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20was%20a%20sharp%20reminder%20of%20his%20responsibilities.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20felt%20very%20good..%20(but)%20I%20realised%20sitting%20there%20that%20I%20have%20to%20live%20up%20to%20the%20expectations%20of%20my%20supporters%20according%20to%20the%20policies%20of%20my%20party%E2%80%A6%20I%20realised%20that%20I%20have%20to%20discharge%20these%20responsibilities%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOutlining%20his%20priorities%2C%20Mr%20Mallik%20said%20he%20wants%20to%20focus%20on%20education%2C%20health%20and%20employment.%20%26quot%3BThese%20three%20basic%20facilities%20should%20be%20provided.%20Education%20in%20schools%20should%20be%20cheap%2C%20irrigation%20should%20also%20be%20cheap...%20this%20is%20what%20I%20want%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20his%20wishlist%20was%20one%20other%20thing.%20%26quot%3BRapid%20rail%20should%20reach%20Muzaffarnagar.%20I%20will%20raise%20these%20issues%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20new%20MP%2C%20who%20has%20acquired%20a%20reputation%20after%20defeating%20Union%20Minister%20and%20BJP's%20prominent%20Jat%20leader%20Sanjeev%20Balyan%20to%20win%20the%20seat.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cstrong%3ELakshmikant%20alias%20Pappu%20Nishad%20from%20Sant%20Kabir%20Nagar%20(Samajwadi%20Party)%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDevelopment%20is%20high%20on%20agenda%20of%20another%20first-time%20MP%20from%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20as%20well.%20%26quot%3BMy%20parliamentary%20area%20is%20quite%20backward%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20former%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20minister%20Lakshmikant%20Pappu%20Nishad.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20very%20few%20basic%20facilities%20like%20roads%2C%20water%2C%20electricity%20in%20Sant%20Kabir%20Nagar.%20%26quot%3BMy%20priority%20will%20be%20to%20put%20the%20aspirations%20of%20people%2C%20my%20supporters%2C%20before%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mr%20Nishad%2C%20who%20handled%20the%20Fertilisers%20and%20Logistics%20departments%20in%20the%20state%20government%20led%20by%20Akhilesh%20Yadav.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERaj%20Kumar%20Sangwan%20from%20Baghpat%20(BJP)%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP's%20new%20MP%20from%20Baghpat%2C%20just%20a%20few%20hours%20away%20from%20the%20national%20capital%2C%20is%20also%20focused%20on%20his%20constituency%2C%20although%20he%20said%20he%20%26quot%3Bfelt%20really%20good'%20on%20his%20first%20day%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%20has%20%26quot%3Bmade%20many%20new%20friends%2C%20met%20many%20old%20friends%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20being%20very%20close%20to%20Delhi%2C%20Baghpat%20is%20a%20backward%20area%2C%20whereas%20Sonipat%20and%20other%20districts%20of%20Haryana%20adjacent%20to%20it%20%26quot%3Bhave%20progressed%20a%20lot%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20priority%20will%20be%20to%20build%20new%20roads%20to%20connect%20Baghpat%20with%20big%20cities%2C%20provide%20better%20education%20and%20health%20facilities%20and%20create%20new%20employment%20opportunities%20for%20the%20youth.%20I%20want%20to%20raise%20issues%20like%20these%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EManoj%20Kumar%20from%20Sasaram%20(Congress)%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20this%20Congress%20MP%2C%20Day%20One%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%20was%20a%20%26quot%3Bhistoric%26quot%3B%20occasion.%20%26quot%3BToday%20I%20went%20to%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20for%20the%20first%20time...%20it%20was%20a%20very%20good%20experience%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Manoj%20Kumar%2C%20who%20is%20representing%20Bihar's%20Sasaram%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2040-year-old%20has%20been%20second-time%20lucky.%20He%20had%20contested%20in%202019%20from%20Mayawati's%20BSP%2C%20but%20could%20not%20dislodge%20the%20BJP's%20Chedi%20Paswan.%20This%20time%2C%20in%20the%20contest%20against%20the%20BJP's%20new%20candidate%20Shivesh%20Kumar%2C%20he%20won%20by%20a%20little%20over%2019%2C000%20votes.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kumar%20said%20unemployment%20remains%20the%20biggest%20issue%20for%20him.%20%26quot%3BEmployment%20for%20the%20youth%20and%20development%20of%20Sasaram%20parliamentary%20constituency%20will%20be%20my%20priority%E2%80%A6%20I%20want%20to%20make%20the%20hill%20in%20Kaimur%20a%20tourist%20spot%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719249720000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2F3pi97tvo_lok-sabha-ani_625x300_24_June_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fgoosebumps-nerves-elation-first-reactions-from-first-time-mps-5961568%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%2018th%20Lok%20Sabha%20convened%20today%2C%20where%20280%20first-time%20MPs%20are%20set%20to%20take%20oath.%20The%20momentous%20occasion%20elicited%20a%20medley%20of%20reactions%20from%20them%20--%20goosebumps%20to%20nervousness%20and%20everything%20in%20between.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2