riat%2C%20Nabanna%2C%20attended%20by%20municipal%20body%20chiefs%2C%20her%20cabinet%20colleagues%20and%20a%20few%20MLAs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSome%20people%20are%20taking%20bribes%20and%20allowing%20encroachment.%20Why%20don't%20you%20understand%20that%20Bengal's%20identity%20is%20being%20tarnished%20because%20you%20people%20are%20taking%20money%3F%20Wherever%20there%20is%20land%2C%20it%20is%20being%20encroached%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20meeting%20assumes%20significance%20as%20the%20ruling%20party%20-%20now%20gearing%20up%20for%20the%20civic%20elections%20that%20are%20to%20be%20held%20in%20the%20state%20next%20year%20-%20was%20trailing%20in%2069%20out%20of%20the%20121%20civic%20bodies%20in%20the%20recent%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%2C%20a%20deeper%20scrutiny%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20results%20shows.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERaking%20up%20the%20issue%20of%20Bengal's%20identity%20being%20tarnished%2C%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BA%20load%20is%20being%20placed%20on%20our%20shoulders.%20After%20this%20the%20state's%20identity%20will%20be%20finished.%20We%20will%20not%20find%20Bengali-speaking%20people%20anymore.%20Everyone%20knows%20Hindi%20and%20English%20today.%20I%20am%20not%20demeaning%20any%20language.%20I%20am%20making%20them%20bigger%20when%20I%20say%20this.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRemember%20each%20state%20has%20its%20own%20identity.%20It%20has%20culture.%20We%20like%20other%20cultures%20too%20and%20respect%20them.%20But%20those%20who%20are%20embroiled%20in%20a%20conspiracy%20to%20spoil%20Bengal's%20identity%2C%20I%20am%20warning%20all%20of%20them%20when%20I%20say%20this.%20In%20exchange%20for%20money%2C%20Bengal's%20identity%20should%20not%20be%20spoilt.%20This%20is%20my%20first%20and%20last%20warning%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20warned.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Trinamool%20Congress%20chief%2C%20who%20is%20in%20charge%20of%20the%20Land%20Department%2C%20recently%20sought%20a%20report%20on%20illegal%20land%20encroachment%20in%20Bengal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGovernment%20property%20and%20land%20are%20being%20encroached%20and%20it%20was%20being%20allowed%20for%20money.%20Government%20property%20is%20not%20anyone's%20private%20property%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20fumed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPulling%20up%20her%20own%20party%20MLA%20and%20state%20minister%20Sujit%20Bose%2C%20she%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BDon't%20listen%20to%20any%20MLA%2C%20MP%2C%20Minister%2C%20DMs.%20Don't%20make%20it%20a%20habit.%20Stop%20making%20money.%20Sujit%20Bose%20is%20here.%20Salt%20Lake%20is%20in%20a%20mess.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESujit%20Bose%20is%20the%20MLA%20of%20Bidhannagar%2C%20also%20known%20as%20Salt%20Lake.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EContinuing%20her%20tirade%2C%20she%20next%20inquired%20about%20the%20Howrah%20district%20magistrate%3A%20%26quot%3BIs%20Howrah%20DM%20here%3F%20Councillors%20are%20not%20there%20and%20MLAs%20are%20taking%20advantage.%20SDOs%20are%20not%20working.%20You%20know%20what%20advantage%20they%20are%20taking.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20will%20not%20allow%20any%20illegal%20activity%20and%20encroachment.%20I%20will%20not%20tolerate%20it%20anymore%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20also%20alleged%20that%20those%20who%20encroached%20land%20%26quot%3Bhave%20voted%20for%20the%20BJP%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurther%20attacking%20the%20Centre%2C%20she%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20central%20government%20is%20selling%20Bengal's%20water.%20They%20built%20Hydel%20projects%20on%20Teesta.%20Earlier%20there%20were%20tripartite%20meetings.%20There%20is%20no%20water%20in%20Teesta.%20They%20think%20just%20because%20they%20have%20won%20north%20Bengal%2C%20they%20will%20do%20whatever%20they%20want.%20They%20are%20selling%20Bengal's%20water.%20I%20will%20write%20a%20strong%20letter%20to%20the%20PM.%20There%20is%20no%20dredging%20in%20Farraka%20and%20now%20Kolkata%20port%20is%20affected.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20built%2014%20dams%20in%20Sikkim%20and%20now%20they%20want%20to%20give%20away%20water%20to%20Bangladesh.%20If%20there%20is%20a%20plan%20to%20deprive%20Bengal%2C%20there%20will%20be%20a%20protest.%20Even%20I%20want%20friendship%20with%20Bangladesh.%20I%20have%20started%20trains%20to%20Bangladesh%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Banerjee%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20letter%20to%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20the%20Bengal%20Chief%20Minister%20had%20objected%20to%20the%20talks%20on%20water%20sharing%20between%20the%20Centre%20and%20Bangladesh.%20%26quot%3BSuch%20unilateral%20deliberations%20and%20discussions%20without%20consultation%20and%20the%20opinion%20of%20the%20state%20government%20is%20neither%20acceptable%20nor%20desirable%26quot%3B%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20rubbished%20Centre's%20proposal%20for%20sharing%20Teesta%20water.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20also%20urged%20the%20PM%20to%20not%20hold%20any%20such%20discussion%20with%20the%20neighbouring%20country%20without%20involving%20the%20West%20Bengal%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20talks%20over%20the%20weekend%2C%20the%20two%20sides%20signed%2010%20agreements%20providing%20for%20bolstering%20ties%20in%20a%20range%20of%20critical%20areas%20such%20as%20digital%20domain%2C%20maritime%20sphere%2C%20blue%20economy%2C%20railways%2C%20space%2C%20green%20technology%2C%20health%20and%20medicine.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20said%20that%20a%20technical%20team%20will%20be%20sent%20to%20Bangladesh%20soon%20for%20a%20mega%20project%20to%20conserve%20and%20manage%20Teesta%20river.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719241740000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Fo2tl5sa8_mamata-banerjee-pti_625x300_24_June_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmamata-banerjee-raps-civic-body-chiefs-do-i-have-to-sweep-streets-now-5960740%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22West%20Bengal%20Chief%20Minister%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20had%20a%20scathing%20question%20for%20the%20state's%20civic%20body%20chiefs