ckquote%3E%20%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHow%20to%20spend%20time%20at%20the%20homestay%3F%20%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20guests%20come%20to%20stay%20with%20us%2C%20they%20usually%20book%20a%20three-night%20stay.%20On%20the%20first%20day%2C%20they%20arrive%20at%20the%20cottage%20by%20the%20afternoon%2C%20usually%20post-lunch%2C%20after%20a%20long%20drive%20from%20places%20like%20Delhi%20or%20Mumbai.%20We%20encourage%20them%20to%20settle%20down%20and%20relax%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Aseem.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20common%20dining%20area%2C%20whether%20it%E2%80%99s%20in%20the%20dining%20room%20or%20the%20terrace%2C%20then%20becomes%20a%20gathering%20spot%20in%20the%20evening.%20%E2%80%9CDuring%20the%20winter%2C%20we%20have%20bonfires%20to%20enhance%20the%20cosy%20atmosphere.%20On%20the%20second%20day%2C%20we%20recommend%20exploring%20the%20local%20sights%20like%20Landour%20and%20the%20Mall%20Road.%20Guests%20often%20spend%20the%20day%20sightseeing%20and%20enjoying%20the%20local%20attractions.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COn%20the%20third%20day%2C%20we%20ask%20the%20guests%20to%20visit%20the%20Benog%20Wildlife%20Sanctuary.%20We%20have%20a%20local%20guide%20who%20is%20very%20knowledgeable%20about%20herbs%20and%20the%20area.%20He%20takes%20the%20guests%20on%20a%20trail%20through%20the%20jungle%20to%20the%20waterfalls.%20Depending%20on%20their%20preference%2C%20the%20trail%20can%20be%20a%20short%20one-hour%20walk%20or%20a%20longer%20four-hour%20hike.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20area%20is%20also%20a%20bird%20sanctuary%2C%20making%20it%20a%20paradise%20for%20bird%20watchers.%20%E2%80%9CMany%20guests%20have%20spotted%20rare%20birds%20such%20as%20the%20blue-throated%20barbet%2C%20plum-headed%20parakeet%2C%20and%20Himalayan%20bulbul%20from%20our%20cottage%2C%20and%20even%20more%20when%20they%20go%20on%20the%20trails.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20morning%20hike%20and%20bird%20watching%2C%20guests%20come%20back%20for%20break