20came%20in.%20As%20Latika%E2%80%99s%20son%20Ninad%20explains%2C%20%E2%80%9CUnder%20any%20climatic%20circumstances%2C%20the%20temperature%20of%20these%20plates%20is%20maintained%20at%2055%20to%2060%20degrees%2C%20which%20helps%20in%20conserving%20the%20nutrients.%E2%80%9D%20He%20adds%20that%20the%20plates%20are%20covered%20by%20UV%20protection%20high-grade%20polycarbonate%20sheets%2C%20which%20also%20protect%20the%20contents%20from%20dust%20and%20external%20particles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20profitability%20gained%20by%20venturing%20into%20solar%20drying%20is%20exponential%2C%20as%20Latika%20shares.%20Not%20only%20does%20it%20reduce%20the%20processing%20time%20of%20the%20fruit%20to%20one%20day%20compared%20to%20three%20to%20four%20days%2C%20she%20says%2C%20but%20it%20also%20increases%20the%20shelf-life%20to%20nine%20months%20from%20the%20previous%20three%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReach%20out%20to%20them%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fauragreenwellness.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E2.%20Solar%20power%20for%20running%20homestays%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fsolar-2-1718974568.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20beautiful%20homestay%20in%20Manali%20is%20powered%20entirely%20by%20solar%20and%20is%20an%20ode%20to%20sustainability%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fsolar-2-1718974568.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fsolar-2-1718974568-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fsolar-2-1718974568-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fsolar-2-1718974568-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fsolar-2-1718974568-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-353861%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20beautiful%20homestay%20in%20Manali%20is%20powered%20entirely%20by%20solar%20and%20is%20an%20ode%20to%20sustainability%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Nitin%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20be%20a%20stretch%20to%20say%20that%20the%20past%20decade%20has%20acted%20as%20an%20inflection%20point%20for%20solar%20power%20in%20the%20housing%20space.%20The%20idea%20gained%20explosive%20traction%2C%20and%20today%2C%20homeowners%20as%20well%20as%20those%20who%20have%20converted%20their%20spaces%20into%20homestays%2C%20are%20favouring%20solar%20power%20over%20traditional%20grid%20dependence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExperts%20are%20of%20the%20opinion%20that%20solar%20panels%20can%20save%20you%20lakhs%20on%20electricity%20bills%20and%20prove%20a%20great%20investment%20in%20the%20long%20run.%20Media%20professional%20Shalini%20whose%20%E2%80%98Raison%20D%E2%80%99etre%E2%80%99%20is%20a%20beautiful%20homestay%20in%20Manali%2C%20recognised%20this%20potential%20early%20on.%20She%20along%20with%20her%20husband%20Nitin%20Beri%20are%20advocates%20of%20sustainable%20living%20and%20were%20keen%20that%20the%20homestay%20be%20a%20symbol%20of%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShalini%20emphasises%20that%20they%20run%20their%20operations%20entirely%20on%20solar%20power%20and%20have%20a%20solar%20system%20in%20place%20that%20generates%20electricity%20on%20which%20the%20entire%20home%20runs.%20%E2%80%9CEven%20on%20days%20when%20there%E2%80%99s%20as%20little%20as%2030%20percent%20sunlight%2C%20the%20system%20works%20efficiently.%20Additionally%2C%20any%20excess%20energy%20generated%20during%20the%20day%20is%20stored%20in%20batteries%2C%20which%20we%20then%20use%20for%20power%20backup%20when%20needed%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Nitin.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReach%20out%20to%20them%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fraisondetremanali%2F%3Fhl%3Den%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E3.%20Solar%20for%20street%20shops%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Ciframe%20referrerpolicy%3D%5C%22strict-origin-when-cross-origin%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FV_X4-pszhBY%3Fsi%3DGx2Wekg4dIYkjvjL%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20we%20speak%2C%20an%20energy%20revolution%20is%20steadily%20brewing%20in%20the%20country%20and%20across%20the%20world.%20According%20to%20data%20by%20Rystad%20Energy%2C%20India%20installed%20a%20record%207.1%20gigawatts%20(GW)%20capacity%20renewable%20energy%20sources%20in%20March%2C%20helping%20the%20country%20reach%20its%20highest-ever%20annual%20installed%20capacity%20of%2018.5%20GW%20in%20FY24.%20And%20this%20marked%20change%20is%20being%20embraced%20across%20sectors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHave%20you%20ever%20avoided%20buying%20produce%20after%20dark%20for%20fear%20of%20not%20being%20able%20to%20notice%20signs%20of%20spoilage%3F%20You%20aren%E2%80%99t%20the%20only%20one.%20But%20when%20this%20practice%20is%20extrapolated%20to%20the%20masses%2C%20it%20has%20an%20impact%20on%20the%20businesses%20run%20by%20street%20vendors.%20They%20find%20themselves%20in%20a%20rush%20to%20sell%20their%20produce%20before%20dusk%2C%20and%20are%20anxious%20about%20the%20produce%20that%20gets%20left%20behind%20as%20it%20will%20be%20discarded.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20Aakarsh%20Shamanur%2C%20a%20Bengaluru-based%20social%20entrepreneur%20noticed%20this%2C%20he%20decided%20to%20bring%20a%20change%20in%20this%20niche%20segment%20using%20the%20power%20of%20solar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20venture%20%E2%80%98Be%20Po-Lite%E2%80%99%20aims%20at%20being%20%E2%80%98a%20ray%20of%20light%E2%80%99%20for%20women%20street%20vendors%20who%20can%20now%20use%20the%203W%20solar-powered%20portable%20lamps%20to%20run%20their%20stalls%20even%20after%20the%20sun%20goes%20down.%20The%20women%20are%20encouraged%20to%20take%20the%20lamps%20home%2C%20use%20them%20for%20cooking%2C%20and%20to%20help%20their%20children%20study.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20multi-purpose%20innovation!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReach%20out%20to%20him%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fbepolite_city%2F%3Fhl%3Den%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E4.%20Solar%20power%20for%20making%20%3Cem%3Erotis%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20article%20posted%20by%20the%20%3Cem%3EMinistry%20of%20New%20and%20Renewable%20Energy%3C%2Fem%3E%20narrated%20the%20story%20of%20two%20women%2C%20Joshi%20and%20Rosy%2C%20who%20used%20solar%20power%20to%20their%20advantage%20to%20create%20thriving%20home%20businesses%20%E2%80%94%20displaying%20an%20appetite%20for%20innovation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Joshi%E2%80%99s%20case%2C%20it%20was%20the%20untimely%20death%20of%20her%20husband%20that%20led%20her%20to%20start%20a%20catering%20business.%20But%20while%20she%20enjoyed%20cooking%2C%20making%20%3Cem%3Erotis%20%3C%2Fem%3E(Indian%20flatbreads)%20was%20proving%20to%20be%20a%20time-consuming%20ordeal%20as%20milling%20the%20flour%20would%20take%20her%20hours%3B%20sometimes%20an%20entire%20day.%20Frequent%20power%20cuts%20were%20of%20no%20help.%20But%20hope%20came%20in%20the%20form%20of%20a%20solar-powered%20rob-rolling%20machine%20and%20a%20flour-milling%20machine.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20same%20success%20was%20tasted%20by%20Rosy%20Louis%20Dabale%20from%20the%20village%20of%20Agsalkatta%20in%20North%20Karnataka.%20Rosy%20is%20a%20health%20worker%20in%20the%20vill