20both%20spiritual%20and%20social%20impact%20programmes%2C%20and%20I%20was%20particularly%20interested%20in%20the%20latter.%20I%20proposed%20and%20organised%20several%20programmes%20for%20them%2C%20one%20of%20which%20was%20my%20first%20volunteering%20project%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENeenu%20suggested%20a%20programme%20which%20became%20the%20foundation%20of%20most%20of%20her%20work%20to%20come.%20%E2%80%9CMy%20plan%20was%20to%20visit%2010%20schools%2C%20plant%20five%20trees%20at%20each%2C%20and%20educate%20the%20students%20on%20the%20importance%20of%20tree%20planting%20and%20environmental%20conservation.%20I%20intended%20to%20take%20up%20about%2045%20minutes%20to%20an%20hour%20of%20their%20time%2C%20focusing%20on%20environmental%20awareness%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Foundation%20agreed%20to%20her%20proposal%20since%20it%20required%20no%20additional%20resources.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20child%20was%20very%20small%20at%20the%20time%2C%20so%2010%20schools%20seemed%20manageable.%20The%20response%20from%20these%20schools%20was%20overwhelmingly%20positive%2C%20and%20soon%20more%20requests%20started%20pouring%20in.%20Within%20three%20months%2C%20I%20managed%20to%20cover%2030%20schools%2C%20which%20was%20my%20maximum%20capacity.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20successful%20project%20became%20her%20motivation%20to%20undertake%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F137931%2Fsocial-impact-fund-infuse-ventures-gold-farm-money%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emore%20social%20impact%20initiatives.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENeenu%20also%20started%20to%20grow%20her%20circle%20and%20started%20volunteering%20and%20designing%20more%20programmes%20for%20different%20organisations.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%202018%2C%20I%20had%20to%20move%20to%20Kochi.%20When%20I%20arrived%2C%20I%20did%20not%20have%20any%20contacts%20in%2